<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFramework>net6.0</TargetFramework>
    <Description>Kledex is a .NET Core framework that can be used to create a simple and clean design by enforcing single responsibility and separation of concerns. Its advanced features are ideal for Domain Driven Design (DDD), Command Query Responsibilty Segragation (CQRS) and Event Sourcing. Kledex also has Azure Service Bus and RabbitMQ integrations.</Description>
